  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "chapterTitle": "总序",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300050368_3_3998-4142",
          "range": "3998-4142",
          "rangeStart": 3998,
          "rangeEnd": 4142,
          "markText": "与其说社会学真的是一门除魅或者灭圣的科学，不如说它其实是一门“扰人的科学”(Bourdieu,1980)。因为它揭露出隐藏在背后的有时被抑制的东西，还因为它经常与统治者的利益相违背，部分由于这些利益隐匿于缄默的表面之下或于情理之后，而情理经常告诉人们事情就应该是这样的且无法是其他的样子。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1721301700,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-07-18 19:21:40",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050368&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3998&rangeEnd=4142",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/31232280813ab7a2cg018789?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3998&rangeEnd=4142"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300050368_3_652-689",
          "range": "652-689",
          "rangeStart": 652,
          "rangeEnd": 689,
          "markText": "布尔迪厄逐渐建立了一种范式，可以总结为“资本”“场域”“惯习”的概念三部曲",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1721301686,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-07-18 19:21:26",
          "chapterUid": 3,
